						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">kbessa wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I've tried with the latest version (snapshot from 2011-07-18), but cannot get it to work, I always get this:</div>
<br />I think the object file version has been changed again, try replacing "original/nes.lib" with nes.lib from this package: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="ftp://ftp.musoftware.de/pub/uz/cc65/snapshot/cc65-snapshot-nes-2.13.9.20110718-1.zip">ftp://ftp.musoftware.de/pub/uz/cc65/sna ... 0718-1.zip</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />Then delete knes.lib and all .o files and run make.
<br />
<br />EDIT: Actually there's also other problem. You changed "cp" to "copy" in the Makefile, so you need to change the forward slash to backward slash or it won't work properly. Change to: copy original\nes.lib knes.lib</div>

					
