						<div class="postbody">I found your tips very informative. I was very happy to see the "force static locals" flag.
<br />
<br />This is using the same compiler flags as your demo make file. Here's the code I used:
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">struct<br />&#123;<br />&nbsp; int x&#91;16&#93;;<br />&nbsp; int y&#91;16&#93;;<br />&nbsp; byte flags&#91;16&#93;;<br />&#125; objects;<br /><br />int main&#40;void&#41;<br />&#123;<br />&nbsp; static byte a;<br />&nbsp; <br />&nbsp; for&#40;a = 0; a &lt; 16; ++a&#41;<br />&nbsp; &#123;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; objects.x&#91;a&#93; = objects.y&#91;a&#93;;<br />&nbsp; &#125;<br />&nbsp; return 0;<br />&#125;</div></div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

